'''Dzawuwu afahyɛ''' yɛ afe afe ammamerɛ ne nnaseɛ [[afahyɛ]] a a ahenfo ne wɔn manfo a wɔn wɔ Agave a ɛwɔ Dabala, wɔ Frao Mantam no di wɔ Ghana. Wodi saa afahyɛ yi wɔ bosome a ɛtɔ so mienu no mu<ref>https://ghanaemberlin.de/travel-tourism/festival/</ref><ref>https://tourghana.com/ghana-festivals/</ref><ref>https://www.slutchtours.com/?page_id=21</ref><ref>https://touringghana.com/festivals/</ref><ref>http://ghanakey.com/ghana-festivals.html</ref><ref>https://www.businessghana.com/site/</ref>.

== Afa hyɛ ==
Wɔ afahyɛ no bere mu no, wɔnoa aduane sorɔnko bi a wɔpete ma abaosom no de srɛ ahobammɔ ma ɔmanfo no<ref>https://myghanaman.com/festivals-in-ghana/</ref>. Wɔgu nsa na amanfo taa wɔn ahenfo no akyi<ref>https://touringghana.com/volta-region/</ref>.

== Mfaso ==
Wodi afahyɛ yi de kae akukuduro a Agavefo no daa no adi wɔ ako ahorɔw a wodii nkunim wɔ mu mfie bi a atwam ko no. Wɔde saa afahyɛ yi nso kae wɔn a w’awu ko no nso<ref>https://www.easytrackghana.com/cultural-overview-ghana-festivals.php</ref>.

